name: Tesseract (itch) (elchirpa)
description:
Tesseract is a dodger game in which you must maneuver through a 10,000-mile field of asteroids that is the only barrier between you and your home.

Collect fuel canisters floating in space to refuel your spaceship and ensure the success of your voyage.
